DOC.TE:
   Sony and Warner have been looking for a buyer for Columbia House
for the last few years. Bertelsmann, which runs a rival music club,
BMG Direct, bought CDNow in 2000 for $117 million.

   Officials in several other cities, including Austin, Texas;
Houston; Myrtle Beach, S.C.; and Chicago, have used public financing
on convention center hotels.
